Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用著一種懷念的溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.98,0:00:29.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹乾流下的淚珠輕拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:39.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.93,0:00:48.10,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.08,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.21,0:00:57.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.99,0:01:13.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使知道不會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那天起 我還是獨自戰鬥至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只希望能夠盡量多殺些幻獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道這只是在逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我想不到其他的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:02:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人背負一切作戰 然後在心中對自己妥協
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.49,0:02:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得這樣就行了 孤單一個人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.39,0:02:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被編到5121部隊時也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次跟你搭乘雙人座機也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是忘不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘不了那個人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人怎麼了嗎？客人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.13,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「最終話  當我說再見時」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(感謝20世紀  2000忘年會)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別好像老頭子一樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼啊 這是忘年會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊 就給它玩個痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是借我們場地 竟然還幫我們做料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.57,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作是慶祝5121部隊被選為休假部隊的禮物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離上次一起休假好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121部隊加藤祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要說出明年的抱負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯喔 宴會部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 明年我還要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多學一點騙經費的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換我森精華了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明年已經是21世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要考到整備技士二級執照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟21世紀有啥關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小舞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是忘年會喔 芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把今年的事情忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是明天喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(再見)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經結束了～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明天是幾點的火車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十點半 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坐巴士 所以隨便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要四點前到博多就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,割草機真方便呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(第一個音跟芝同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舞～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香菇真是好吃呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(第一個字跟舞同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也夠了吧速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算消沉到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人就是會被女人甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被踢開也不受打擊的話 有時女方也會自己回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊 今年是我們最後見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的願意這個樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是忘不了呢 忘不了那個人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經有結論了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就說客觀的意見好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該去8312部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊可以充分發揮你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以下是身為司令官的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.39,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們來說 你離開的話 我們的戰力難免會降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了我們部隊 我希望你能留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請在過年後給我答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以司令官的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及為了我們的部隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你個人又怎麼認為呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這要由她自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 小志還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小陽跟小隆要我來看小志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說你可能被陰乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小志 小舞就拜託你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞說她不回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.29,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以學校裏只剩下小志跟小舞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞她很怕寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小志 就拜託你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(坦白一點吧 愛情獵人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年也受您照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣 望望美麻煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼之後的事情就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心 一路保重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要走 為什麼二話不說就走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真纏人 別跟來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.48,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 您先吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我小時候很膽小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.26,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被叫去買東西 也不敢跟店員講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道何時 我下定決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「打擾了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「小久 歡迎啊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼至今都辦不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 我是速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以用這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被留在戰場的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時我說了唯一的謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是那一種喜歡 只是對他有所憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的好喜歡他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}請設定時間
