Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}相信大家都各有所思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}為了紀念這歷史的瞬間
